Interface GTUSetInt<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GTUMap, GTUSet

    public interface GTUSetInt<T>
    This interface is the base of set class and others that implement it. It includes all the necessary basic methods for a simple set.

    • Method Summary
